1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2694:\"\n<p>O WordPress 5.8.2 est√° dispon√≠vel!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Esta vers√£o de seguran√ßa e manuten√ß√£o apresenta <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?id=54129%2C54323%2C54207&amp;milestone=5.8.2&amp;group=component&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=owner&amp;col=type&amp;col=status&amp;col=priority&amp;col=milestone&amp;order=priority\">2 corre√ß√µes de erros</a>, al√©m de <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/54207\">1 corre√ß√£o de seguran√ßa</a>. Como este √© um <strong>lan√ßamento de seguran√ßa</strong>, √© recomend√°vel que voc√™ atualize seus sites imediatamente. Todas as vers√µes desde o WordPress 5.2 tamb√©m foram atualizadas.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>O WordPress 5.8.2 √© um lan√ßamento com foco em seguran√ßa e manuten√ß√£o. O pr√≥ximo lan√ßamento principal ser√° a vers√£o 5.9.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Voc√™ pode baixar o WordPress 5.8.2 em WordPress.org ou visite seu Painel ‚Üí Atualiza√ß√µes e clique em Atualizar agora. Se voc√™ tiver sites que suportam atualiza√ß√µes autom√°ticas em segundo plano, eles j√° iniciaram o processo de atualiza√ß√£o.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Para obter mais informa√ß√µes, navegue na <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?id=54129%2C54323%2C54207&amp;milestone=5.8.2&amp;group=component&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=owner&amp;col=type&amp;col=status&amp;col=priority&amp;col=milestone&amp;order=priority\">lista completa de altera√ß√µes</a> no Trac ou verifique a p√°gina de <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/wordpress-version/version-5-8-2/\">documenta√ß√£o do HelpHub da vers√£o 5.8.2</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"agradecimentos\">Agradecimentos</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A vers√£o 5.8.2 foi liderada por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/desrosj/\">Jonathan Desrosiers</a> e <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/circlecube/\">Evan Mullins</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Al√©m da equipe de lan√ßamento mencionada acima, agradecemos a todos que ajudaram a fazer o WordPress 5.8.2 acontecer:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aristath/\">Ari Stathopoulos</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bradleyt/\">Bradley Taylor</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/davidwebca/\">davidwebca</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/circlecube/\">Evan Mullins</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gziolo/\">Greg Zi√≥≈Çkowski</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/desrosj/\">Jonathan Desrosiers</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jrf/\">Juliette Reinders Folmer</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mukesh27/\">Mukesh Panchal</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sergeybiryukov/\">Sergey Biryukov</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/shimon246/\">shimon246</a> e <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/fierevere/\">Yui</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"WP Translation Day 2021: Participe do dia internacional de tradu√ß√£o do WordPress no Brasil!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://br.wordpress.org/2021/09/14/wp-translation-day-2021/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://br.wordpress.org/2021/09/14/wp-translation-day-2021/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 14 Sep 2021 21:51:51 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s