controu um erro, publique na √°rea <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/forum/alphabeta/\">alfa/beta</a> dos f√≥runs de suporte. Gostar√≠amos muito de ouvir de voc√™! Se voc√™ se sentir confort√°vel em escrever um <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/reports/\">relat√≥rio de erro</a> reproduz√≠vel, envie um para o <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/newticket\">WordPress Trac</a>. Aqui tamb√©m √© onde voc√™ pode encontrar uma lista de <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/tickets/major\">erros conhecidos</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Agradecemos a <em><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/desrosj/\">@desrosj</a> e <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/clorith/\">@clorith</a> pela revis√£o e a <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/chanthaboune/\">@chanthaboune</a> pelos cr√©ditos finais.</em></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"WordPress 5.8 Beta 3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"https://br.wordpress.org/2021/06/23/wordpress-5-8-beta-3/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 23 Jun 2021 12:29:24 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Lan√ßamentos\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"5.8\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"x